= Slides for Modern Web Apps with HTML5 Web Components and Polymer, Java EE MVC and JAX-RS

Originally presented at JavaOne 2015

Kito Mann, http://www.virtua.com[Virtua, Inc.^]

== Viewing

These slides are in pure HTML -- just view javaee-mvc-and-polymer.html and you're good to go!

You can also view them online (http://kito99.github.io/polymer-javaee-mvc-todo[html] or http://kito99.github.io/polymer-javaee-mvc-todo/java-ee-mvc-and-polymer.pdf[pdf]).

== Building

The presentation slides are plain HTML and http://lab.hakim.se/reveal-js/#/[reveal.js^], built using  http://asciidoctor.org[Asciidoctor^]. To generate all of the HTML slides, execute the included Grunt build script:

----
grunt
----

To run a server or run examples, execute:

----
grunt server
----

